---
import PageHeader from "../../../components/PageHeader.astro";
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";

const title = "Nguon du lieu";
const description = "Ket noi nhieu nguon du lieu trong NocoBase va quan ly du lieu doanh nghiep tu mot giao dien duy nhat.";
const keywords = "NocoBase, nguon du lieu, CRM, ERP, tich hop du lieu, workflow";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} keywords={keywords}>
  <PageHeader title={title}>
    <span slot="description">{description}</span>
  </PageHeader>
  <section class="section"><div class="container">
    <div class="row align-items-top "><div class="col-lg-5 col-md-5"><div class="section-title"><h5 class="mb-4">Ket noi <span class="text-primary">nhieu nguon du lieu</span> va quan ly du lieu doanh nghiep tai mot noi</h5><p class="text-muted">Du lieu thuong nam rải rac trong CRM, ERP, tai chinh va ton kho. Khi ket noi tat ca voi NocoBase, ban co the tich hop va truy van du lieu tren mot giao dien duy nhat, giam viec chuyen doi he thong, pha vo silo du lieu va giam chi phi bao tri.</p></div></div><div class="col-lg-7"><div class="card rounded border-0 shadow ms-lg-5"><video controls class="rounded shadow"><source src="https://static-docs.nocobase.com/DS-1.1-EN.mp4" type="video/mp4"></video></div></div></div>
    <div class="row align-items-top mt-100"><div class="col-lg-5 col-md-5"><div class="section-title"><h5 class="mb-4">Ket noi cac nguon du lieu khac nhau o frontend bang <span class="text-primary">luong su kien</span></h5><p class="text-muted">Khi mot trang co cac block den tu nhieu nguon du lieu, luong su kien co the dieu phoi su tuong tac giua chung ngay tren giao dien. Vi du, khi xem mot khach hang trong CRM, ban co the dong thoi xem lich su don hang tu ERP.</p></div></div><div class="col-lg-7"><div class="card rounded border-0 shadow ms-lg-5"><video controls class="rounded shadow"><source src="https://static-docs.nocobase.com/DS-1.2-EN.mp4" type="video/mp4"></video></div></div></div>
    <div class="row align-items-top mt-100"><div class="col-lg-5 col-md-5"><div class="section-title"><h5 class="mb-4">Ket noi cac nguon du lieu khac nhau o backend bang <span class="text-primary">workflow</span></h5><p class="text-muted">Khi mot ung dung NocoBase su dung nhieu nguon du lieu, workflow co the dieu phoi logic giua chung o backend va tu dong hoa quy trinh lien he thong. Vi du, khi tao don hang moi trong ERP, cap do khach hang tuong ung trong CRM co the duoc cap nhat tu dong.</p></div></div><div class="col-lg-7"><div class="card rounded border-0 shadow ms-lg-5"><video controls class="rounded shadow"><source src="https://static-docs.nocobase.com/DS-1.3-EN.mp4" type="video/mp4"></video></div></div></div>
  </div></section>
</Layout>
